{"tid":2438134,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[圖表派］SPX喇叭型冇人講","createTime":"2021-03-08T09:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T13:47:02.000Z","uid":320177,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a9db411c19ecb49f69bd1d4845c10501bdda27","tid":2438134,"uid":320177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"廢話唔講，先睇SPX月線圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hh7J5Ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhh7J5Ue.png&h=b9155990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自2018年尾，spx都係大喇叭入面行左2年半，<br />\n直至11月尾升穿喇叭頂<br />\n<br />\n而升穿後，喇叭頂亦一直支持SPX上升<br />\n可以睇以下日線圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXY5zPc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXY5zPc.png&h=5fca4239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持線分別係<br />\n12月23<br />\n1月4<br />\n2月1<br />\n3月5<br />\n支持spx 彈高<br />\n<br />\n咁今晚即係升定跌？<br />\n圖表都唔知，<br />\n但圖表黎講<br />\n跌穿3月5低位，跌機會大啲<br />\n守係喇叭頂的話，升機會大啲<br />\n<br />\n如果今晚跌穿喇叭頂，<br />\n圖表話最有可能會跌到大約3200點<br />\n<br />\n至於3200係咪有力，<br />\n要睇指數去到有冇轉勢，<br />\n有轉勢先好入市，<br />\n等市場證明比你睇果個支持位有力，<br />\n唔好嘗試用支持位黎摸底同接飛刀。<br />\n<br />\n以上內容只係TA角度<br />\n入市前請用FA加以判斷"},{"pid":"9c1878fd84556e8cebc8deefe41d6c30ff927602","tid":2438134,"uid":84926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:01:06.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n升就會升<br />\n跌就會跌<br />\n低買高賣未輸過"},{"pid":"311506541485691f7764740aea5ec061547d3c5f","tid":2438134,"uid":69083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"樓主走先 我頂著 連登仔最憎圖表派"},{"pid":"217274211b0b48d7b87d1d9c2a04038d86c01c03","tid":2438134,"uid":320177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"311506541485691f7764740aea5ec061547d3c5f","tid":2438134,"uid":69083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"樓主走先 我頂著 連登仔最憎圖表派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:05:29.00